The '''Ballista Tower''' is a building in [http://lordofultima.wikia.com/wiki/Lord_of_Ultima Lord of Ultima]. It increases the Defensive Value of a limited number of Ballistae by 100%. If there are not enough Ballistae in the city, 10 City Guards can take each allotted slot and gain the same [http://lordofultima.wikia.com/wiki/Ballista_Tower# bonus]. These towers don't count towards a city's building number limit.

<p style="margin-top:0.4em;margin-bottom:0.5em;">'''Requirements:''' [http://lordofultima.wikia.com/wiki/Town_Hall Town Hall] Level 9</p>

